title: Kate Winslet & Michael Fassbender Glam Up 'Steve Jobs' Closing Night Gala
text: Kate Winslet and co-star Michael Fassbender bring Hollywood glam to the Closing Night Gala of their new movie the Steve Jobs during England’s BFI London Film Festival held at Odeon Leicester Square on Sunday (October 18). PHOTOS: Check out the latest pics of Kate Winslet Danny Boyle, pictured inside, directed the film while Aaron Sorkin [...] »
